{"tid":1895324,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特：11歲已開始買股　周一冧市「是好消息」","createTime":"2020-02-24T12:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T04:36:12.000Z","uid":123587,"like":332,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4320b59baa2f6a896981818681bda053113a86","tid":1895324,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，「股神」巴菲特在接受訪問時表示，自己在11歲的時候已開始買股票，當時沒有理會股市狀況，整體來說是每年也「淨買入」，但不是每日買股，也有高追過個別股份，但次數很少。<br />\n<br />\n至於目前全球股市關注新冠肺炎疫情進展，他指出，其投資決定不是「逐日睇」，每日的新聞頭條不能幫助你買股，只要有機會，就可趁低買入心儀股份。<br />\n<br />\n被問到美股道指周一(24日)有機會甫開市就大跌逾800點，巴菲特直言，「這是好消息，是趁低入貨時機。」"},{"pid":"e209f595870bf51cbd759a63e67bf6dc67df86ff","tid":1895324,"uid":103759,"like":61,"dislike":5,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你死廢老"},{"pid":"85eb0ec46e54b9d046da0c6670a6a44393b5918f","tid":1895324,"uid":316420,"like":159,"dislike":4,"score":155,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />11歲買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我15歲先開始買 唔怪得發達冇我份"},{"pid":"f77a3321c31e1eb8c785f8bf2627d92710dddb58","tid":1895324,"uid":60393,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"股神都要唱好出貨啦"},{"pid":"264953f01b9caca50ee1481e2a662be4c953f98d","tid":1895324,"uid":70619,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"唔唱好點出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cc5650123804378b9d50453d77dc838101eb6f","tid":1895324,"uid":146285,"like":68,"dislik